verbose_text: In addition, RhoA and ROCK1 proteins were more significantly activated in the 48 h group compared with the 24 h group (P < 0.05), and NRG-1 was able to significantly inhibit the activation of RhoA and ROCK in the two groups (P < 0.05).
evidence: NRG-1 was able to significantly inhibit the activation of RhoA
